name: Part of the "Peacefeet Calm Before the Storm" collection.
description:
These "Peacefeet" handmade flowers are made from a patterned material with a felted back support. Some flowers have a stitched button face. All sitting pretty on an elastic band. Easy to put on. You can wear them with some types of sandals and flip flops. Preference and cute-ness raised worn on their own.
Moody foot flowers.
